          before other lessons. The nursery and primary section conducts assembly daily, while the college 
          section conducts assembly on Mondays.</p>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 1.7rem; text-align: justify;">At nealy 7:30 am, the college students begin their day with <i>azkar</i> for about 10 minutes.
          Also, a <b>general class</b> has been introduced for students where some important topics are discussed
          with the students. The general class is conducted on Sundays, Tuesdays, and Wednesdays. It is 
          immediately after the <i>azkar</i> and last form about 15 minutes.</p>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 1.7rem; text-align: justify;">The nursery and primary students come out for their first break at 10:00 am and return to their
